---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Icon from '../../components/Icon.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  currentPage="tools"
  title="老虎機 RTP 實測紀錄器｜記錄你的回報率，用數據判斷平台有沒有動手腳 - GAME8LA"
  description="別聽明牌，看你自己的數據。輸入每次投注的投入與回收金額，系統自動算出你的實測 RTP，搭配官方理論值比對，一眼看出平台有沒有偷降回報率。"
>
<div class="container">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <div class="rtp-hero">
    <h1><Icon name="bar-chart" /> 老虎機 RTP 實測紀錄器</h1>
    <p class="rtp-slogan">別聽明牌，看你自己的數據。</p>
    <p class="rtp-desc">輸入每次遊戲的投入與回收金額，系統幫你算出實測回報率，跟官方 RTP 比對。紀錄越多次越準——如果你的數字長期低於理論值，那問題可能不在運氣。</p>
  </div>

  <div class="rtp-layout">
    <!-- ===== 左欄：輸入區 ===== -->
    <div class="rtp-input-panel">
      <h2>📝 新增紀錄</h2>

      <label class="rtp-label">選擇遊戲</label>
      <select id="gameSelect" class="rtp-select">
        <option value="" disabled selected>-- 選擇遊戲 --</option>
      </select>
      <div id="customGameWrap" style="display:none;margin-top:0.5rem">
        <input type="text" id="customGameName" class="rtp-input" placeholder="輸入遊戲名稱" />
        <input type="number" id="customGameRtp" class="rtp-input" placeholder="官方 RTP %（例如 96.5）" step="0.01" min="0" max="100" style="margin-top:0.4rem" />
      </div>

      <div id="gameArticleLink" style="display:none;margin:0.5rem 0">
        <a id="gameArticleAnchor" href="#" style="color:var(--guava-green);font-size:0.85rem;font-weight:600">📖 查看這款遊戲的完整攻略 →</a>
      </div>

      <label class="rtp-label" style="margin-top:1rem">💰 投入金額（NT$）</label>
      <input type="number" id="inputBet" class="rtp-input" placeholder="例如：2000" min="1" step="1" />

      <label class="rtp-label">💵 回收金額（NT$）</label>
      <input type="number" id="inputReturn" class="rtp-input" placeholder="例如：1350" min="0" step="1" />

      <label class="rtp-label">📅 日期</label>
      <input type="date" id="inputDate" class="rtp-input" />

      <label class="rtp-label">📝 備註（選填）</label>
      <input type="text" id="inputNote" class="rtp-input" placeholder="例如：買了兩次免遊" maxlength="50" />

      <button id="btnAdd" class="rtp-btn-add" onclick="addRecord()">＋ 新增這筆紀錄</button>

      <div class="rtp-io-row">
        <button class="rtp-btn-io" onclick="exportTXT()"><Icon name="download" /> 匯出備份</button>
        <label class="rtp-btn-io" style="cursor:pointer"><Icon name="upload" /> 匯入備份<input type="file" id="importFile" accept=".txt,.json" style="display:none" onchange="importBackup(event)" /></label>
        <button class="rtp-btn-io rtp-btn-danger" onclick="clearAll()"><Icon name="trash-2" /> 清除</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ===== 右欄：結果區 ===== -->
    <div class="rtp-result-panel">
      <!-- 統計摘要 -->
      <div class="rtp-stats-row">
        <div class="rtp-stat-card">
          <span class="rtp-stat-label">累積紀錄</span>
          <span class="rtp-stat-value" id="statCount">0</span>
          <span class="rtp-stat-unit">筆</span>
        </div>
        <div class="rtp-stat-card">
          <span class="rtp-stat-label">總投入</span>
          <span class="rtp-stat-value" id="statBet">0</span>
          <span class="rtp-stat-unit">元</span>
        </div>
        <div class="rtp-stat-card">
          <span class="rtp-stat-label">總回收</span>
          <span class="rtp-stat-value" id="statReturn">0</span>
          <span class="rtp-stat-unit">元</span>
        </div>
        <div class="rtp-stat-card rtp-stat-highlight">
          <span class="rtp-stat-label">實測 RTP</span>
          <span class="rtp-stat-value" id="statRtp">--</span>
          <span class="rtp-stat-unit">%</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 動態警示 -->
      <div id="rtpAlert" class="rtp-alert" style="display:none"></div>

      <!-- 折線圖 -->
      <div class="rtp-chart-wrap">
        <canvas id="rtpChart"></canvas>
        <p class="rtp-chart-note">橫軸：累積紀錄筆數 ｜ 綠色實線：你的實測 RTP ｜ 金色虛線：官方理論 RTP</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 紀錄表格 -->
      <h3 style="margin-top:1.5rem">📋 歷史紀錄</h3>
      <div class="rtp-table-wrap">
        <table class="rtp-table" id="recordTable">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>日期</th>
              <th>遊戲</th>
              <th>投入</th>
              <th>回收</th>
              <th>單次 RTP</th>
              <th>累積 RTP</th>
              <th></th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody id="recordBody"></tbody>
        </table>
        <p id="emptyMsg" class="rtp-empty">還沒有紀錄。在左邊輸入你的第一筆數據吧。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Casino Check CTA -->
  <section class="casino-check-cta" style="margin-top:2rem">
    <div class="cta-icon">🛡️</div>
    <h3>實測 RTP 偏低？先查查平台有沒有問題</h3>
    <p>如果你的實測回報率長期低於官方 RTP 超過 10 個百分點，問題可能不在運氣——有些平台會用魔改版遊戲偷降 RTP。入金前查一下 165 黑名單和網域年齡。</p>
    <a href="/casino-check/" class="cta-check-btn">🔎 前往娛樂城體檢 — 免費即時檢測</a>
  </section>

  <!-- 使用說明 -->
  <div class="rtp-faq">
    <h3>💡 怎麼用這個工具？</h3>
    <div class="card" style="margin:1rem 0">
      <p><strong>1. 每次玩完一個 session 就記一筆</strong>——不需要記每一轉，只要記「這次坐下來投了多少、最後拿回多少」就好。</p>
      <p><strong>2. 紀錄越多越準</strong>——5 筆的時候波動很大，50 筆以上才開始有參考價值。100 筆以上你的曲線會明顯趨近某個數字，那就是你在這個平台的真實 RTP。</p>
      <p><strong>3. 跟官方 RTP 比對</strong>——圖表上的金色虛線是該遊戲的官方理論 RTP。如果你的綠色實線長期在虛線下方很遠（差超過 10%），這台可能不是正版。</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:0"><strong>4. 數據存在你的瀏覽器裡</strong>——我們不會上傳你的任何資料。想備份或換裝置的話，按「匯出備份」會下載一個 .txt 檔，傳到新裝置後按「匯入備份」選那個檔案就能還原。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="guava-note" style="margin-top:1rem">
      <p>🌿 <strong>芭樂子提醒：</strong>RTP 是長期統計指標，短期波動很正常。玩了 10 次算出 RTP 120% 不代表你找到了金雞母，玩了 10 次算出 60% 也不代表一定是黑網——樣本量不夠大的時候，什麼數字都有可能出現。耐心記錄，讓數據自己說話。</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="text-align:center;margin:2rem 0">
    <a href="/" class="btn-outline">&larr; 回首頁</a>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Chart.js CDN -->
<script is:inline src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Chart.js/4.4.1/chart.umd.min.js"></script>

<script is:inline>
// ===== 遊戲資料庫 =====
var GAMES = [
  { name: '戰神賽特', rtp: 96.5, article: '/articles/atg-seth-guide/' },
  { name: '戰神賽特 2', rtp: 97.2, article: '/articles/atg-seth-1-vs-2-comparison/' },
  { name: '麻將胡了', rtp: 96.5, article: '/games/game-5/' },
  { name: '麻將胡了 2', rtp: 96.5, article: '/games/game-8/' },
  { name: '奇幻魔藥', rtp: 98.28, article: '/games/fantasy-potion/' },
  { name: '魔龍傳奇', rtp: 96.0, article: '/games/game-3/' },
  { name: '雷神之鎚', rtp: 96.5, article: '/games/thor-hammer-2/' },
  { name: '贏財神', rtp: 96.5, article: '/games/caishen-wins/' },
  { name: '戰神呂布', rtp: 96.0, article: null },
  { name: '寶石之星', rtp: 96.5, article: null },
  { name: '其他遊戲（自訂）', rtp: null, article: null, custom: true },
];

var STORAGE_KEY = 'game8la_rtp_tracker';
var records = [];
var chart = null;

// ===== 初始化 =====
(function init() {
  // 填充遊戲選擇器
  var sel = document.getElementById('gameSelect');
  GAMES.forEach(function(g, i) {
    var opt = document.createElement('option');
    opt.value = i;
    opt.textContent = g.custom ? g.name : g.name + '（RTP ' + g.rtp + '%）';
    sel.appendChild(opt);
  });
  sel.addEventListener('change', onGameChange);

  // 設定日期預設值為今天
  var today = new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0];
  document.getElementById('inputDate').value = today;

  // 從 localStorage 讀取
  try {
    var saved = localStorage.getItem(STORAGE_KEY);
    if (saved) records = JSON.parse(saved);
  } catch(e) {}

  renderAll();
})();

function onGameChange() {
  var idx = parseInt(document.getElementById('gameSelect').value);
  var game = GAMES[idx];
  var customWrap = document.getElementById('customGameWrap');
  var articleLink = document.getElementById('gameArticleLink');
  var articleAnchor = document.getElementById('gameArticleAnchor');

  if (game && game.custom) {
    customWrap.style.display = 'block';
  } else {
    customWrap.style.display = 'none';
  }

  if (game && game.article) {
    articleAnchor.href = game.article;
    articleAnchor.textContent = '📖 查看「' + game.name + '」完整攻略 →';
    articleLink.style.display = 'block';
  } else {
    articleLink.style.display = 'none';
  }
}

// ===== 新增紀錄 =====
function addRecord() {
  var selIdx = document.getElementById('gameSelect').value;
  if (selIdx === '') return alert('請先選擇遊戲');

  var game = GAMES[parseInt(selIdx)];
  var gameName, gameRtp;

  if (game.custom) {
    gameName = document.getElementById('customGameName').value.trim();
    gameRtp = parseFloat(document.getElementById('customGameRtp').value);
    if (!gameName) return alert('請輸入遊戲名稱');
    if (isNaN(gameRtp) || gameRtp <= 0 || gameRtp > 100) return alert('請輸入合理的官方 RTP（0～100）');
  } else {
    gameName = game.name;
    gameRtp = game.rtp;
  }

  var bet = parseFloat(document.getElementById('inputBet').value);
  var ret = parseFloat(document.getElementById('inputReturn').value);
  var date = document.getElementById('inputDate').value;
  var note = document.getElementById('inputNote').value.trim();

  if (isNaN(bet) || bet <= 0) return alert('請輸入有效的投入金額');
  if (isNaN(ret) || ret < 0) return alert('請輸入有效的回收金額');
  if (!date) return alert('請選擇日期');

  records.push({
    id: Date.now(),
    date: date,
    game: gameName,
    rtp: gameRtp,
    bet: bet,
    ret: ret,
    note: note
  });

  saveAndRender();

  // 清空輸入（保留遊戲選擇和日期）
  document.getElementById('inputBet').value = '';
  document.getElementById('inputReturn').value = '';
  document.getElementById('inputNote').value = '';
}

// ===== 刪除紀錄 =====
function deleteRecord(id) {
  records = records.filter(function(r) { return r.id !== id; });
  saveAndRender();
}

// ===== 儲存 + 重新渲染 =====
function saveAndRender() {
  try {
    localStorage.setItem(STORAGE_KEY, JSON.stringify(records));
  } catch(e) {}
  renderAll();
}

// ===== 渲染全部 =====
function renderAll() {
  renderStats();
  renderAlert();
  renderTable();
  renderChart();
}

// ===== 統計摘要 =====
function renderStats() {
  var totalBet = 0, totalRet = 0;
  records.forEach(function(r) { totalBet += r.bet; totalRet += r.ret; });
  var rtp = totalBet > 0 ? (totalRet / totalBet * 100) : 0;

  document.getElementById('statCount').textContent = records.length;
  document.getElementById('statBet').textContent = Math.round(totalBet).toLocaleString();
  document.getElementById('statReturn').textContent = Math.round(totalRet).toLocaleString();
  document.getElementById('statRtp').textContent = records.length > 0 ? rtp.toFixed(1) : '--';

  // 顏色
  var rtpEl = document.getElementById('statRtp');
  if (records.length === 0) {
    rtpEl.style.color = 'var(--text-muted)';
  } else if (rtp >= 100) {
    rtpEl.style.color = '#39FF14';
  } else if (rtp >= 90) {
    rtpEl.style.color = '#f5b800';
  } else {
    rtpEl.style.color = '#ef4444';
  }
}

// ===== 動態警示 =====
function renderAlert() {
  var el = document.getElementById('rtpAlert');
  if (records.length < 3) {
    el.style.display = 'none';
    return;
  }

  var totalBet = 0, totalRet = 0;
  var avgTheoRtp = 0;
  records.forEach(function(r) {
    totalBet += r.bet;
    totalRet += r.ret;
    avgTheoRtp += r.rtp;
  });
  avgTheoRtp = avgTheoRtp / records.length;
  var actualRtp = totalBet > 0 ? (totalRet / totalBet * 100) : 0;

  el.style.display = 'block';

  if (actualRtp > 110) {
    el.className = 'rtp-alert rtp-alert-win';
    el.innerHTML = '🎉 <strong>目前處於運氣爆發期</strong>（實測 ' + actualRtp.toFixed(1) + '%）。恭喜！但記得設好停利線，手氣不會永遠這麼好。';
  } else if (actualRtp >= 100) {
    el.className = 'rtp-alert rtp-alert-ok';
    el.innerHTML = '✅ <strong>目前回報率高於 100%</strong>（實測 ' + actualRtp.toFixed(1) + '%）。短期內你是贏的，但長期 RTP 會往理論值收斂，不要上頭。';
  } else if (actualRtp >= avgTheoRtp - 10) {
    el.className = 'rtp-alert rtp-alert-ok';
    el.innerHTML = '📊 <strong>實測 RTP 在合理範圍內</strong>（' + actualRtp.toFixed(1) + '% vs 理論 ' + avgTheoRtp.toFixed(1) + '%）。繼續累積數據，紀錄越多越準。';
  } else if (actualRtp >= avgTheoRtp - 15 || records.length < 20) {
    el.className = 'rtp-alert rtp-alert-warn';
    el.innerHTML = '⚠️ <strong>實測 RTP 偏低</strong>（' + actualRtp.toFixed(1) + '% vs 理論 ' + avgTheoRtp.toFixed(1) + '%）。' + (records.length < 20 ? '目前紀錄只有 ' + records.length + ' 筆，樣本量不夠，先繼續記錄觀察。' : '建議再多記幾次，如果持續偏低就要注意了。');
  } else {
    el.className = 'rtp-alert rtp-alert-danger';
    el.innerHTML = '🚨 <strong>警告：你的實測回報率遠低於理論值</strong>（' + actualRtp.toFixed(1) + '% vs 理論 ' + avgTheoRtp.toFixed(1) + '%，差距 ' + (avgTheoRtp - actualRtp).toFixed(1) + ' 個百分點）。已累積 ' + records.length + ' 筆紀錄，這個差距不太可能只是運氣問題。建議確認你玩的平台是不是正版。<br><a href="/casino-check/" style="color:#fff;font-weight:700;text-decoration:underline">→ 點我查詢該平台是否曾被檢舉</a>';
  }
}

// ===== 紀錄表格 =====
function renderTable() {
  var tbody = document.getElementById('recordBody');
  var emptyMsg = document.getElementById('emptyMsg');

  if (records.length === 0) {
    tbody.innerHTML = '';
    emptyMsg.style.display = 'block';
    return;
  }

  emptyMsg.style.display = 'none';

  // 計算累積 RTP
  var cumBet = 0, cumRet = 0;
  var rows = records.map(function(r) {
    cumBet += r.bet;
    cumRet += r.ret;
    var singleRtp = r.bet > 0 ? (r.ret / r.bet * 100) : 0;
    var cumRtp = cumBet > 0 ? (cumRet / cumBet * 100) : 0;
    return { ...r, singleRtp: singleRtp, cumRtp: cumRtp };
  });

  // 倒序顯示（最新在前）
  var html = '';
  for (var i = rows.length - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
    var r = rows[i];
    var sColor = r.singleRtp >= 100 ? '#39FF14' : r.singleRtp >= 85 ? '#f5b800' : '#ef4444';
    html += '<tr>' +
      '<td>' + r.date + '</td>' +
      '<td>' + r.game + '</td>' +
      '<td>$' + Math.round(r.bet).toLocaleString() + '</td>' +
      '<td>$' + Math.round(r.ret).toLocaleString() + '</td>' +
      '<td style="color:' + sColor + ';font-weight:700">' + r.singleRtp.toFixed(1) + '%</td>' +
      '<td>' + r.cumRtp.toFixed(1) + '%</td>' +
      '<td><button class="rtp-btn-del" onclick="deleteRecord(' + r.id + ')" title="刪除">✕</button></td>' +
      '</tr>';
  }
  tbody.innerHTML = html;
}

// ===== Chart.js 折線圖 =====
function renderChart() {
  var ctx = document.getElementById('rtpChart');
  if (!ctx) return;

  if (records.length === 0) {
    if (chart) { chart.destroy(); chart = null; }
    return;
  }

  // 計算累積 RTP 序列
  var cumBet = 0, cumRet = 0;
  var labels = [];
  var dataPoints = [];
  var theoLine = [];
  var avgTheoRtp = 0;
  records.forEach(function(r) { avgTheoRtp += r.rtp; });
  avgTheoRtp = avgTheoRtp / records.length;

  records.forEach(function(r, i) {
    cumBet += r.bet;
    cumRet += r.ret;
    labels.push('#' + (i + 1));
    dataPoints.push(cumBet > 0 ? +(cumRet / cumBet * 100).toFixed(2) : 0);
    theoLine.push(+avgTheoRtp.toFixed(2));
  });

  var config = {
    type: 'line',
    data: {
      labels: labels,
      datasets: [
        {
          label: '你的實測 RTP',
          data: dataPoints,
          borderColor: '#39FF14',
          backgroundColor: 'rgba(57,255,20,0.1)',
          borderWidth: 2.5,
          pointRadius: records.length > 30 ? 0 : 4,
          pointBackgroundColor: '#39FF14',
          tension: 0.3,
          fill: false,
        },
        {
          label: '官方理論 RTP',
          data: theoLine,
          borderColor: '#f5b800',
          borderWidth: 2,
          borderDash: [8, 4],
          pointRadius: 0,
          tension: 0,
          fill: false,
        }
      ]
    },
    options: {
      responsive: true,
      maintainAspectRatio: false,
      plugins: {
        legend: {
          labels: { color: '#ccc', font: { size: 12 } }
        },
        tooltip: {
          callbacks: {
            label: function(ctx) {
              return ctx.dataset.label + ': ' + ctx.parsed.y.toFixed(1) + '%';
            }
          }
        }
      },
      scales: {
        x: {
          ticks: { color: '#999', maxTicksLimit: 15 },
          grid: { color: 'rgba(255,255,255,0.05)' }
        },
        y: {
          ticks: {
            color: '#999',
            callback: function(v) { return v + '%'; }
          },
          grid: { color: 'rgba(255,255,255,0.08)' },
          suggestedMin: Math.max(0, Math.min.apply(null, dataPoints) - 15),
          suggestedMax: Math.max.apply(null, dataPoints) + 10,
        }
      }
    }
  };

  if (chart) {
    chart.data = config.data;
    chart.options = config.options;
    chart.update();
  } else {
    chart = new Chart(ctx, config);
  }
}

// ===== 匯出 TXT 備份 =====
function exportTXT() {
  if (records.length === 0) return alert('沒有紀錄可匯出');
  var encoded = btoa(unescape(encodeURIComponent(JSON.stringify(records))));
  var content = 'GAME8LA-RTP:' + encoded;
  var blob = new Blob([content], { type: 'text/plain;charset=utf-8' });
  var url = URL.createObjectURL(blob);
  var a = document.createElement('a');
  a.href = url;
  a.download = 'game8la-RTP紀錄器-備份-' + new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0] + '.txt';
  a.click();
  URL.revokeObjectURL(url);
}

// ===== 匯入備份（支援 .txt 和 .json）=====
function importBackup(event) {
  var file = event.target.files[0];
  if (!file) return;
  var reader = new FileReader();
  reader.onload = function(e) {
    var raw = e.target.result.trim();
    var imported;
    try {
      // 嘗試 1：GAME8LA-RTP: 前綴的 Base64 格式（txt）
      if (raw.indexOf('GAME8LA-RTP:') === 0) {
        var b64 = raw.substring(12);
        var decoded = decodeURIComponent(escape(atob(b64)));
        imported = JSON.parse(decoded);
      } else {
        // 嘗試 2：直接 JSON 格式
        imported = JSON.parse(raw);
      }
      if (!Array.isArray(imported)) throw new Error('格式錯誤');
      imported.forEach(function(r) {
        if (!r.game || !r.bet || r.ret === undefined || !r.rtp || !r.date) throw new Error('資料欄位不完整');
      });
      var merged = records.concat(imported);
      var seen = {};
      records = merged.filter(function(r) {
        if (!r.id) r.id = Date.now() + Math.random();
        if (seen[r.id]) return false;
        seen[r.id] = true;
        return true;
      });
      saveAndRender();
      alert('成功匯入 ' + imported.length + ' 筆紀錄！');
    } catch(err) {
      alert('匯入失敗：檔案格式不正確。請選擇從本工具匯出的 .txt 或 .json 備份檔。');
    }
  };
  reader.readAsText(file);
  event.target.value = '';
}

// ===== 清除全部 =====
function clearAll() {
  if (!confirm('確定要清除所有紀錄嗎？此操作無法復原。')) return;
  records = [];
  saveAndRender();
}
</script>

